text: Assens is a municipality in Gros-de-Vaud in the canton of Vaud in Switzerland. The community decided to merge their municipality with Malapalud, with effect from 1 January 2009.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz published by the Swiss Federal Statistical Office accessed 18 February 2011. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Gros-de- Vaud
